  ext/exif/exif.c script when parsing JPEG EXIF entries|affected=PHP versions 5.4.x before 5.4.37, 5.5.x before 5.5.21, and
  5.6.x before 5.6.5.|impact=Successful exploitation will allow remote attackers to cause a
  denial of service or possibly execute arbitrary code via different crafted dimensions.|solution=Update to PHP version 5.4.37, 5.5.21, 5.6.5 or later.|vuldetect=Checks if a vulnerable version is present on the target host.|solution_type=VendorFix</tags>
